<body>
  <h1>Markdown Cheatsheet</h1>

  <h2>Headings</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Heading 1</td><td><code># Heading 1</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Heading 2</td><td><code>## Heading 2</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Heading 3</td><td><code>### Heading 3</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Text Formatting</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Bold</td><td><code>**bold text**</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Italic</td><td><code>*italic text*</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Strikethrough</td><td><code>~~strikethrough~~</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Inline Code</td><td><code>`inline code`</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Lists</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Unordered list</td><td><code>- Item 1<br>- Item 2</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Ordered list</td><td><code>1. First<br>2. Second</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Links and Images</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Link</td><td><code>[title](https://example.com)</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Image</td><td><code>![alt text](image.jpg)</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Blockquotes</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Quote</td><td><code>&gt; This is a blockquote</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Code Blocks</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Fenced code block</td><td><code>```<br>code here<br>```</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Language‑specific block</td><td><code>```python<br>print("Hello")<br>```</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Tables</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Description</th><th>Syntax</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Basic table</td><td><code>| Column 1 | Column 2 |<br>|----------|----------|<br>| Data 1   | Data 2   |</code></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Glossary</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Term</th><th>Explanation</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Heading</td><td>Titles created with <code>#</code> symbols. More <code>#</code> = smaller heading.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Bold</td><td>Text wrapped in <code>**</code> for emphasis.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Italic</td><td>Text wrapped in <code>*</code> for lighter emphasis.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Inline Code</td><td>Short snippets wrapped in backticks <code>`like this`</code>.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Fenced Code Block</td><td>Multi‑line code wrapped in triple backticks <code>```</code>.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Blockquote</td><td>Quoted text starting with <code>&gt;</code>.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>List</td><td>Bulleted with <code>-</code> or numbered with <code>1.</code>.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Link</td><td>Clickable text using <code>[title](url)</code>.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Image</td><td>Embedded picture using <code>![alt](path)</code>.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Table</td><td>Rows and columns defined with <code>|</code> and <code>-</code>.</td></tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
